{"tid":2220974,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"當到達8點鐘 節目開始 大亨屌到陳到仆街","createTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T11:23:06.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c975d57431bf583369299622edebfda05a7c7a8d","tid":2220974,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"錢課開（大香港早晨）<br />\n<br />\n 我把錢箱關起來只留下一張廿蚊<br />\n 這樣的大香港早晨我對著大亨發呆<br />\n 看著時事一幕一幕<br />\n 首次演出熱時節目<br />\n 我把電視機打開聽著大香港早晨<br />\n 也許大亨陳到可以給我一個交代<br />\n 你要準備我學不來<br />\n 眼睜眼節目變壞<br />\n 人怔怔看情感慨<br />\n 不能給你準備我還你廿蚊<br />\n 安靜收聲也是另一種對待<br />\n 當到達8點鐘<br />\n 節目開始<br />\n 大亨屌到陳到仆街<br />\n 我給你最後的疼愛是罰廿蚊<br />\n 不要studio中間隔著一片海<br />\n 陳到的污點就留給時間慢慢漂白<br />\n 把廿蚊收進檯面錢箱<br />\n 最後的疼愛是手放開<br />\n 不想用言語拉扯所以選擇不責怪<br />\n 熱時就像候車月台有人走有人來<br />\n 陳到心是一個站牌<br />\n 寫著等待"},{"pid":"2e1ed7e00418339f1031fc088ef1cc9a64e93dc5","tid":2220974,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"410ba6599eb3fe75ff6609657473fcca6fc5a70e","tid":2220974,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD38tDD.gif&amp;h=3fa76e4c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPsihh0.gif&amp;h=37a4f6c2&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD38tDD.gif&amp;h=3fa76e4c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPsihh0.gif&amp;h=37a4f6c2&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD38tDD.gif&amp;h=3fa76e4c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPsihh0.gif&amp;h=37a4f6c2&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD38tDD.gif&amp;h=3f